  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2644",
  "title": "[theme] appearance doesn't get prefixed",
  "body": "see http://shouldiprefix.com/#appearance, `-webkit-appearance: none` is necessary on selects and inputs to make them look normal. This doesn't seem to be applied by our autoprefixer\r\n\r\nnow| with `-webkit-appearance: none`\r\n---|---\r\n<img width=\"210\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-12-29 at 16 26 12\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6270048/34440363-099c1500-ecb5-11e7-955c-6ef85558392d.png\"> | <img width=\"187\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-12-29 at 16 26 07\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6270048/34440379-15fb8768-ecb5-11e7-8adc-f4fe12beb372.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\nIIRC this was fixed by writing the prefix manually in input[type=search]",
